text: Karen Fukuhara (born February 10, 1992) is an American actress. She is known for her roles as Katana in the 2016 DC superhero movie Suicide Squad and as The Female in the 2019 Amazon Prime original series The Boys. She is also known for voicing the character Glimmer in the Netflix series She-Ra and the Princesses of Power. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from Los Angeles
